lead_paragraph: England head coach Eddie Jones has leapt to the defence of George Ford, despite the flyhalf failing to convert six of his seven shots at goal during England's 27-13 victory over Wales at Twickenham on Sunday.

headline.main: Jones Voices Support for Ford After Woeful Kicking Display
headline.print_headline: Jones Voices Support for Ford After Woeful Kicking Display
